text:
We were only there for 45 mins as Google says it closes at 2am.

They had a number of song selections so that was great and the room price comes with a beer tower.

Definitely worth a try and hope to have a better experience next time!
Entered the location and was told immediately by an angry Indian man that “this is not a bar” while whooshing us out of the door.

Around 10 person sit together inside got many sound lock rooms with AC can drink and have TV any kind of karaoke music will play and have one mic we can sing behind the played karokke well with full sound can laughf clapping etc...
Love the drinks & company, do what you want.
Not a good hang out place with bad service and interior looks old.
